4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge aiming to pursue a career as cybersecurity specialists. The program encompasses a comprehensive curriculum covering Windows and Linux administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management using DLP strategies. It spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 16. Participants receive an official completion certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes can be conducted in English or Spanish, based on the campus's language choice. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop